      "role": "user",
      "content": "meditation isnt gonna fix a sharp headache lol. look i know u have to say the disclaimer thing but i just want to know if it's actually dangerous or if u guys just say that to be safe. my neighbor takes both and she's fine. i just want to take one and go to bed, is it really gonna cause a major bleeding issue if it's just one single dose?",
